        <Parent_String>flasks (bottles) [300045671], bottles by form [300206788], bottles [300045627], vessels (containers) [300193015], containers by form [300194507], containers (receptacles) [300197197], Containers (hierarchy name) [300045611], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
